.\" kilonode/docs/man/kilonode-msg.1
.Dd May 26, 2026
.Dt KILONODE-MSG 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm kilonode-msg
.Nd manage a local KiloNode message store
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl -store Ar path
.Ar command
.Op Ar arguments
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a local developer and admin tool for KiloNode-native message stores.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl -store Ar path
Use the message store rooted at
.Ar path .
.It Fl -help
Show command usage.
.El
.Sh COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Cm init
Initialize store directories.
.It Cm create-private Ar from Ar to Ar subject Ar bodyfile
Create a private message.
.It Cm create-bulletin Ar from Ar area Ar subject Ar bodyfile
Create a bulletin.
.It Cm list
List non-deleted messages.
.It Cm read Ar id
Read message metadata and body.
.It Cm delete Ar id
Soft-delete a message.
.It Cm reindex
Rebuild message indexes.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa var/messages
Example local store path.
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Dl kilonode-msg --store /tmp/kilonode-msg-test init
.Dl kilonode-msg --store /tmp/kilonode-msg-test list
.Sh SECURITY NOTES
Do not point the store at untrusted shared directories. Message contents are
treated as hostile input.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr kilonode-store 1 ,
.Xr kilonode-user 1
.Sh AUTHORS
KiloNode is developed by M6VPN.
